{
  "message": "test: expand fuzz corpus for ntm_importer, tuning_config, string_parsers\n\n- ntm_importer_json: 4 new seeds (workflow with triggers/steps,\n  full config with safety/robot/hooks, multi-session with nested\n  windows/panes, null literal)\n- tuning_config_toml: 3 new seeds (all 13 sections with edge-case\n  zero/minimal values, type mismatches for error paths, unknown\n  sections for forward-compat)\n- string_parsers: 5 new seeds (openai slug, claude model string,\n  CRITICAL/ErRoR/info severity levels for case-insensitive matching)\n\nAll 9 fuzz targets now have 6-12 corpus seeds.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
